    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CORPOREAL</strong> is a photographic horror investigation game where you piece together a cursed family photo album. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the sole survivor of unexplained events in 1990s New Zealand, you search for answers in an archive of photographs recovered from the ruins of your childhood home. Examine haunted photographs, encounter the paranormal and uncover your dark family history.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE AN ANALOG ARCHIVE</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/71383612e639749078aca2fca5d989be.poster.avif?t=1760497221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/71383612e639749078aca2fca5d989be.webm?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/71383612e639749078aca2fca5d989be.mp4?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXAMINE HAUNTED PHOTOGRAPHS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/e5369acfd66ef91ea29d2c2804f49c1f.poster.avif?t=1760497221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/e5369acfd66ef91ea29d2c2804f49c1f.webm?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/e5369acfd66ef91ea29d2c2804f49c1f.mp4?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE A PARANORMAL MYSTERY</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/37eed3aeaeafb3ac61dfee035a9eb8e0.poster.avif?t=1760497221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/37eed3aeaeafb3ac61dfee035a9eb8e0.webm?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255140/extras/37eed3aeaeafb3ac61dfee035a9eb8e0.mp4?t=1760497221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Examine </strong>live-action<strong> </strong>photographs to reveal hidden secrets &amp; spectres.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deduce</strong>  when photos were taken &amp; the order of events.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate</strong> a family archive through tactile analog interfaces.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel</strong> a paranormal-mystery set in mid-90s New Zealand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul></p>",
